author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 45
acceptance_criteria: Empty or whitespace-only --title rejected on create and update; error shape matches the missing-required-option error; regression tests; GH-533 closed
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Resolved with shared trim-then-require title validation used by create and update.
expected_result: Empty and whitespace-only titles fail before persistence with the required-title usage error.
actual_result: Create and update reject blank titles with exit 2 while legacy malformed fixture reads remain covered.
